In the next episode, we'll
explore what the latest DNA

00:29:22.690 --> 00:29:25.890 align:middle line:84%
studies are now revealing
when it comes to our origin.

00:29:25.890 --> 00:29:28.510 align:middle line:84%
And while some of our questions
are going to be answered,

00:29:28.510 --> 00:29:30.220 align:middle line:84%
I have to tell you
right now, we'll

00:29:30.220 --> 00:29:33.040 align:middle line:84%
also find that the
answers that we do receive

00:29:33.040 --> 00:29:35.800 align:middle line:84%
are going to open up the door
to an even deeper mystery

00:29:35.800 --> 00:29:38.230 align:middle line:84%
and forbidden
territory when it comes

00:29:38.230 --> 00:29:40.810 align:middle line:84%
to modern science
and the human story.

